sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/System
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS 1.2+
    participant Webhook as Validation Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS mTLS
    participant Controller as modelmesh-controller<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    participant etcd as etcd<br/>2379/TCP HTTP/HTTPS<br/>TLS optional
    participant S3 as S3/MinIO Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>AWS SigV4
    participant Service as ModelMesh Service<br/>8033 gRPC / 8008 HTTP
    participant RESTProxy as REST Proxy<br/>8008/TCP
    participant ModelMesh as ModelMesh<br/>8085/TCP gRPC
    participant Adapter as Runtime Adapter<br/>8001/TCP gRPC
    participant Runtime as Model Server<br/>8001/TCP gRPC
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>Metrics collection

    Note over User,Runtime: Flow 1: Model Deployment
    User->>K8sAPI: Create Predictor/ServingRuntime CR<br/>HTTPS/6443 Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: Validate CR<br/>HTTPS/9443 mTLS
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validation result
    K8sAPI-->>User: CR created
    K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch event (CR created)
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Deployment + Service<br/>HTTPS/6443 ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>etcd: Store runtime config<br/>HTTP/2379

    Note over S3,Runtime: Flow 2: Model Loading
    Adapter->>S3: Pull model artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443 AWS SigV4
    S3-->>Adapter: Model files
    Adapter->>Runtime: Load model into memory<br/>gRPC/8001
    Runtime-->>Adapter: Model loaded
    Adapter->>ModelMesh: Register model<br/>gRPC/8085
    ModelMesh->>etcd: Update routing table<br/>HTTP/2379
    etcd-->>ModelMesh: Confirmed

    Note over User,Runtime: Flow 3: Inference Request (gRPC)
    User->>Service: POST /v2/models/model:predict<br/>gRPC/8033 mTLS optional
    Service->>ModelMesh: Forward inference request<br/>gRPC/8085
    ModelMesh->>Adapter: Route to model<br/>gRPC/8085
    Adapter->>Runtime: Execute inference<br/>gRPC/8001
    Runtime-->>Adapter: Prediction result
    Adapter-->>ModelMesh: Response
    ModelMesh-->>Service: Response
    Service-->>User: Prediction result

    Note over User,Runtime: Flow 3b: Inference Request (REST)
    User->>RESTProxy: POST /v2/models/model/infer<br/>HTTP/8008 TLS optional
    RESTProxy->>ModelMesh: Translate to gRPC<br/>gRPC/8033
    ModelMesh->>Adapter: Route to model<br/>gRPC/8085
    Adapter->>Runtime: Execute inference<br/>gRPC/8001
    Runtime-->>Adapter: Prediction result
    Adapter-->>ModelMesh: Response
    ModelMesh-->>RESTProxy: gRPC response
    RESTProxy-->>User: JSON response

    Note over Controller,Prometheus: Flow 4: Metrics Collection
    Prometheus->>Controller: Scrape /metrics<br/>HTTPS/8443 ServiceAccount Token
    Controller-->>Prometheus: Controller metrics
    Prometheus->>ModelMesh: Scrape /metrics<br/>HTTP/2112
    ModelMesh-->>Prometheus: Runtime metrics
